#!/usr/local/bin/perl

=head1 NAME

spoc1 - First pass of Netspoc

=head1 SYNOPSIS

spoc1 [options] [in-directory | in-file] [CODE-DIR]

=head1 OPTIONS

See options of program 'netspoc'.

=back

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Compile all files from 'in-directory' or from a single 'in-file' or from STDIN.
Intermdiate code is generated in CODE-DIR.
If no CODE-DIR is given, no code is generated; only errors are checked.

